ial\">&nbsp;</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=Arial size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">I am going to </SPAN></FONT><FONT face=Arial size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">China</SPAN></FONT><FONT face=Arial size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"> on Sunday till following Saturday, coming back into </SPAN></FONT><FONT face=Arial size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">Paris</SPAN></FONT><FONT face=Arial size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"> on Saturday evening. Are you staying in Paris then ? Meet up ? P</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\" size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">&nbsp;</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\" size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">&nbsp;</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\" size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">&nbsp;</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\" size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">&nbsp;</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\" size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">&nbsp;</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><STRONG><B><I><FONT face=Arial size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-STYLE: italic; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">The Rt. Hon.</SPAN></FONT></I></B></STRONG><STRONG><B><I><FONT face=Arial size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-STYLE: italic; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">Peter Mandelson</SPAN></FONT></I></B></STRONG></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><EM><I><FONT face=Arial size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">European Commissioner for Trade</SPAN></FONT></I></EM></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\" size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">&nbsp;</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><EM><I><FONT face=Arial size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">Tel: 00322 295 6881</SPAN></FONT></I></EM></P>\n<P class=MsoNor